org.sensorhub.impl.service.wsn

Class NotificationSystem

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sensorhub.impl.service.wsn.NotificationSystem
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    SPSNotificationSystem

    public class NotificationSystem
extends Object
    Helper class to send notification messages in the WS-Notification format. It relies on the Apache MUSE library version 2.2.0.
    Author:
    Alex Robin

      • setMaxSubscriptionLength

        public void setMaxSubscriptionLength(long subscriptionLength)
        Sets the initial duration of all subscriptions after which they are removed from the DB. This is a service wide value but users can increase the duration of their subscriptions by renewing their subscription.
        Parameters:
        subscriptionLength - max subscription duration in seconds. Use the UNLIMITED_DURATION constant for unlimited duration.
